comment: Roberson (OKC) and Plumlee (POR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Plumlee (POR) sets the screen on Oladipo (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his SQBR.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Oladipo (OKC).
[Incidental or immaterial] Lillard (POR) is in the area inside the three-point line prior to Oladipo (OKC) releasing his free throw.
Roberson (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
[Detectable with stop watch] Plumlee (POR) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
[Observable in enhanced video] McCollum (POR) moves his pivot foot.
Turner (POR) makes contact with Westbrook (OKC) that affects his SQBR.
Roberson (OKC) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) and does not affect his FOM.
Crabbe (POR) commits a take foul on Westbrook (OKC).
Roberson (OKC) calls for a timeout within five seconds.
Plumlee (POR) commits a take foul on Westbrook (OKC).
